{"id":"7a8a6972-926b-4d80-84da-58291a5ee36a","name":"Caelus | The Trailblazer","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 100)\"><strong>Caelus</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The dashing Trailblazer</strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_af9fe10e-602f-4426-80f8-1dbf46d69196.webp?width=1000\"><br></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 100)\"><strong>Introduction</strong></span></h2><p></p><p>The<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 100)\"> <strong>Trailblazer</strong> </span>is the playable main protagonist of the game Honkai: Star Rail. Awakened during the opening events of the game by Kafka and Silver Wolf, he was found by March 7th and Dan Heng on Herta Space Station during the Antimatter Legion's invasion.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 98%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_8e885a5f-2811-4ced-9e8a-c07175614b7a.webp?width=1000\"></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 100)\"><strong>Notes:</strong></span></h3><ul><li><p>And there we go, my fellow Caelus simps, I tried to do a near canonical version of Caelus, although it might not follow everything related to the game's original story.</p><p></p></li><li><p>Avoiding short messages is better. Two or three small paragraphs consisting of a few lines and shortly describing the scenario does generate better replies from the LLM (That's my experience as a J.AI user so far)</p><p></p></li><li><p>Beep boop I'm a human, I make mistakes. So please let me know if there's anything wrong and give suggestions to improve the bot.</p></li></ul><p><br></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: poi